<td style=" color:#000000; font-size:12pt; background-color:#FFFFFF; font-family:arial; bLabel:main; bEditID:r3st1;" tEditID="c1r1" locked="0" aEditID="c1r1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Dear {!Contact.Name},<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">We have received the original bank mandate for&nbsp;<span style="background-color: white;">IATA&nbsp;<strong>{!Case.Country__c}</strong></span>.<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Your request is being processed. Kindly reminding you to keep your current bank details active until IATA will send you a confirmation that the bank account change has been successfully carried out, including the settlement date in which the new instruction will be effective.<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Please be advised that we will be running a Penny Test, therefore please provide the applicable contact persons details who will be accountable to provide us the penny test's confirmation (if you have not done so&nbsp;already). A Penny Test is when IATA will proceed&nbsp;with a settlement of 1 penny (or 1 cent, depending of the market) to the airline's new bank account and track the payment with the Clearing Bank. Once we run a successful penny test, the new bank account would be used for the next potential airline's settlements. Such process will bring more security for the airlines' financial and cash flow availability.</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">We will contact you shortly.<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Kind Regards,<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Case.OwnerFullName}<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Global Airline Participation Team<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Financial and Distribution Services<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">International Air Transport Association (IATA)<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">33, Route de l' Aeroport<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">1215 Geneve<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Switzerland<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><a href="http://www.iata.org/"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">www.iata.org</font></a></p>]]></td>
